          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You step into the clearing that Tollin has utilized as his studio, and find the young sculptor surrounded by shimmering and shifting sculptures of kinetic glass. You look more closely and see that some of the sculptures are actually three-dimensional landscape portraits of the ancient Estian buildings scattered around the Valley."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Tollin Lang is bent over a thick dolewood bole that he\u2019s turned into a worktable. He seems to be messing around with a collection of flowsteel plates arranged in a row."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "em",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "span",
              "items": [
